& [InferenceJobResult] is outside preservation proposal
 + [focus] is worker’s reliability claim
 + [inside] is two successful isolated runs on same prompt family
 + [boundary] is only those specific runs count as evidence
 + [outside] is outside uncertainty unsupported boundary
 + [inference] is claim not fully supported by broader testing
 + [caution] is avoid generalizing beyond the tested scope
 + [next_step] is conduct additional diverse prompt evaluations
